/p><p>在其他地方，亚马逊雄心勃勃的<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lord-of-the-rings-the-rings-of-power-was-amazon-primes-most-watched-debut-ever-075410830.html"><em>《指环王：权力之戒》</em></a>获得了六项提名（主要是在技术类别）。 Netflix 的<em>《怪奇物语》</em>获得六项提名，《孔雀的<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/poker-face-season-one-preview-160035861.html"><em>扑克脸》</em></a>获得四项提名， <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/star-trek-picard-3-10-the-last-generation-review-140006372.html"><em>《星际迷航：皮卡德》</em></a>获得两项化妆提名。 HBO 以 127 项提名领先所有平台，而 Netflix 以 103 项提名领先于纯流媒体网络，其次是苹果（52 项）和亚马逊（46 项）。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-emmys-are-reportedly-delayed-due-to-ongoing-strikes-164958589.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-emmys-are-reportedly-delayed-due-to-ongoing-strikes-164958589.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5613b92c-5369-43c0-873f-bee7acaf57bb</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jul 2023 16:49:58 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690563000</ingested><modified> 2023-07-28T16:50:06+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Television]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1394" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/72e4e600-2d63-11ee-baef-105abc83a10b" width="2482"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:descripti